Third-party notice
------------------

This MIT license covers the source code in this repository only.

The optional YOLO backend (`method="yolo"`) imports Ultralytics at runtime and
downloads YOLO11 weights (e.g. yolo11n.pt) on first use. Ultralytics and its
model weights are licensed under AGPL-3.0, NOT MIT. If you use the YOLO
backend, your usage is subject to Ultralytics' AGPL-3.0 terms (or a separate
Ultralytics Enterprise License).

The default, dependency-light `method="opencv"` backend uses only NumPy (BSD)
and OpenCV (Apache-2.0) and is free for closed-source commercial use.
